Analisis ROC para 4 GS a 3 diferentes concentraciones

dt<-subset(nicot,select=c("n250 UFC","n500 UFC","n1000 UFC","dias cambio","n250_R2UFC","n500_r2UFC","n1000_r2UFC","PZA  MGIT","sec_KV","PZA_ KV","Wyn_KV","stn comp","PZA  MGIT"))
colnames(dt) <- make.names(colnames(dt), unique=TRUE)
dt$stn.comp<-as.integer(dt$stn.comp)
dt$Wyn_KV<-as.integer(dt$Wyn_KV)
dt$sec_KV<-as.integer(dt$sec_KV)

col<-c("roc1"="springgreen3", "roc2"="dodgerblue3","roc3"="khaki2","roc4"="indianred3")
linetype<-c("a"="solid","b"="dashed","c"="dotted","d"="twodash")
lab1<-c("stn.comp","Wyn_KV","sec_KV","PZA MGIT")
lab2<-c("n250","n500","n1000")
(r2<-ggplot() + 
  
  geom_roc(aes(d = Wyn_KV, m = n250_R2UFC, color="roc2",linetype="a"),dt,alpha.point = 0, labels = F) + 
  geom_roc(aes(d = Wyn_KV, m = n500_r2UFC, color="roc2",linetype="b"),dt,alpha.point = 0, labels = F) + 
  geom_roc(aes(d = Wyn_KV, m = n1000_r2UFC, color="roc2",linetype="c"),dt,alpha.point = 0, labels = F) + 
    
  geom_roc(aes(d = sec_KV, m = n250_R2UFC, color="roc3",linetype="a"),dt,alpha.point = 0, labels = F) + 
  geom_roc(aes(d = sec_KV, m = n500_r2UFC, color="roc3",linetype="b"),dt,alpha.point = 0, labels = F) + 
  geom_roc(aes(d = sec_KV, m = n1000_r2UFC, color="roc3",linetype="c"),dt,alpha.point = 0, labels = F) + 
    
  geom_roc(aes(d = stn.comp, m = n250_R2UFC, color="roc1",linetype="a"),dt,alpha.point = 0, labels = F) + 
  geom_roc(aes(d = stn.comp, m = n500_r2UFC, color="roc1",linetype="b"),dt,alpha.point = 0, labels = F) + 
  geom_roc(aes(d = stn.comp, m = n1000_r2UFC, color="roc1",linetype="c"),dt,alpha.point = 0, labels = F) + 
  
  geom_roc(aes(d = PZA..MGIT, m = n250_R2UFC, color="roc4",linetype="a"),dt,alpha.point = 0, labels = F) + 
  geom_roc(aes(d = PZA..MGIT, m = n500_r2UFC, color="roc4",linetype="b"),dt,alpha.point = 0, labels = F) + 
  geom_roc(aes(d = PZA..MGIT, m = n1000_r2UFC, color="roc4",linetype="c"),dt,alpha.point = 0, labels = F) + 
    
  scale_color_manual(values=col,
                     name="color legend",label=lab1, guide="legend") + 
  scale_linetype_manual(values=linetype,label=lab2,guide="legend") +
  style_roc())

   scale_color_manual(values=col_d,name="color legend",label=lab_d, guide="legend") + 
   style_roc())
